org.safs.rest.service

Class Service

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.rest.service.Service

  • public class Service
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the information needed to test a specific web service.

    A test or ongoing interactive session with a specific web service will have a unique service Id and all information associated with that interactive service session will be retained here.

    Author:
    Carl Nagle
